review_blob: 4.8% of yuck. Beer has a very artifical malty/soghrum flavor. The after taste has a "Equal" sweetner flavor.  I let one get to around 55 degrees and it started tasting better than it did cold. Maybe thats it......nah. Add another $1.50-$2.00 and get a much better beer (any beer).
beer_name: Tap Room No. 21 Moes Backroom Lager
